    Verse: 9
Tags:
  - Cause & Effect
---
A thought of anger or hatred sends arrows from the mental factory towards
the person aimed at, hurts the individual, sets up discord and disharmony
in the thought-world, and comes back again to the sender and harms the
sender also.
